  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hip fractures are usually classified according to their X-ray as subcapital, pertrochanteric.
      We examine hip fractures with ultrasound in order to characterize the fractures with several
      parameters.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
